{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_10_03",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 3話 また熱ですか",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――公演初日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Opening Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.1400000334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ舞台の本番ですね……\nドラマの撮影前とは、なんだか違った緊張感です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ it's the real stage performance…\nIt's a different kind of tension compared to filming a drama.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "本番までにいろいろあったからなぁ……\n優があんなに演技に手こずるとは思わなかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A lot happened before opening night…\nI never thought Yu would struggle so much with acting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3800908487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも風邪で倒れちゃいましたね\n今はもう、どっちも完全復活しましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san also collapsed with a cold.\nBut now both are completely recovered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……面目次第もございません\nもう、あのような醜態は晒さないようにいたします……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm deeply ashamed of myself.\nI shall not display such disgraceful behavior again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.7120180845
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、すみれは元々演技がうまかったけど\n今日までの間に、さらに磨きがかかったよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ Sumire was already good at acting‚\nbut your skills have been further refined until today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われるとなんだか照れちゃいますね\nうーん……本を読んだり、いろいろ勉強もしましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being told that makes me feel embarrassed.\nHmm… I read books and studied various things‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2612469435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの看病をして\n本の内容を実感出来たのが良かったんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but by taking care of {user}-san‚\nI could truly experience what I had read‚ and I think that was valuable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.1932897012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん現実では、今回のアニメとか舞台みたいに\n不思議な力でぱっと病気を治せる訳じゃないですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ in reality‚ unlike this anime or stage play‚\nyou can't instantly cure illness with mysterious powers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5440154155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "患者さんを見守って、元気になってくれた時は\nこんなに嬉しいんだなって分かったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ watching over patients and seeing them get better\nBut‚ watching over patients and seeing them get better",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.3571901084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。あの後、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんにも\n{user}さんが倒れたことを話したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. After that‚ I also told Rui-chan and Yu-chan\nabout {user}-san collapsing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんは慌ててお見舞いを持っていこうとしたので\n「もう治ってる」って止めたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan panicked and tried to bring get-well gifts‚\nso I stopped her saying \"he's already better.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0683312682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.2502740623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんは……\n「惜しいことしたなぁ～」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Yu-chan said…\n\"Too bad I missed it~\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "「そんなん役作りにも生かせるし、おもろいし\n最高のイベントやん」って言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"That could really help with role preparation‚ and it sounded fun too—\"\n\"that's such a perfect event~\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.6215474687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "優のやつ、喉元過ぎればって感じだな……\n稽古中はあんなにどん底みたいな顔をしてたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu… It's like \"danger past‚ God forgotten\"…\nDuring rehearsals she looked like she was at rock bottom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……経験を演技に生かすのは大事ということで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… using experience for acting is important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7590980452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3173292718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "でも「おもろい」って言うくらいだし、優に看病して\nもらったら、寝込んでる間もからかってきそうだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But since Yu says it's \"interesting‚\" If she took care of me‚\nshe'd probably tease me even while I'm bedridden…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんはそんな子じゃないですよ\n病人をイジメて困らせるようなことはしません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan isn't that kind of person.\nShe wouldn't bully and trouble a sick person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2668964943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "悪い悪い。……風邪は、俺のただの自己管理不足だけど\nみんなの役に立ったなら、良かったと思っておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. …The cold was just my poor self-management‚\nbut if it helped everyone‚ I'll think of it as good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.256873123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もう倒れるまで無理しちゃダメですからね\n夜に残業しなくてもいいように効率よく仕事して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you can't overdo it until you collapse anymore.\nPlease work efficiently so you don't have to work overtime at night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.1333329518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "い、一番難しいことをおっしゃる……\n――あ。そろそろ幕が上がるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you're asking for the most difficult thing…\n――Oh. It looks like the curtain will rise soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1333329518,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3106.187446799993,
          "startTime": 146.0666662852
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.5273494324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよですね\n……それじゃあ、みんなを元気にしてきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally.\n…Well then‚ I'll go cheer everyone up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数ヶ月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several Months Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5158300957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 157.6891634147
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 157.6891634147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、まさかあの舞台を円盤化してもらえるなんて\nお客さんの応援あってこそですし、嬉しいですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ I never thought that stage play would be made into a disc.\nIt's thanks to the audience's support‚ and I'm happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。あの舞台は、トリエルのキャラ再現度も\n凄かったって、評判が良かったからな",
      "translations": {
